<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>OTP Verification | Wander Trip</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: "Arial", sans-serif;
        background-color: #f8f9fa;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        color: #333;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 30px auto;
        background: white;
        border-radius: 10px;
        overflow: hidden;
        box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }
      .header {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3a7bd5, #00d2ff);
        color: white;
        padding: 40px 20px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .header h1 {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 32px;
        font-weight: bold;
      }
      .header p {
        margin: 10px 0 0;
        font-size: 16px;
      }
      .content {
        padding: 40px 30px;
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }
      .content h2 {
        font-size: 24px;
        margin-bottom: 16px;
      }
      .otp-box {
        background: #e0f0ff;
        border: 3px dashed #007bff;
        border-radius: 12px;
        padding: 40px 20px;
        text-align: center;
        margin: 40px 0;
        box-shadow: inset 0 0 12px rgba(0, 123, 255, 0.15);
      }
      .otp {
        font-size: 52px;
        font-weight: 900;
        color: #007bff;
        letter-spacing: 20px;
        background: #fff;
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 20px 30px;
        border-radius: 12px;
        box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0, 123, 255, 0.25);
        user-select: all;
        font-family: "Courier New", monospace;
      }
      .footer {
        background: #f1f3f5;
        padding: 25px 20px;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 13px;
        color: #666;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>Travel Smarter, Experience More</h1>
        <p>Your journey begins here</p>
      </div>

      <div class="content">
        <h2>Hello, <%= fullName %></h2>
        <p>
          Thank you for signing up with <strong>Wander Trip</strong>. To
          complete your account verification, please enter the following OTP
          code:
        </p>

        <div class="otp-box">
          <div class="otp"><%= otp %></div>
        </div>

        <p>
          This code will expire in <strong>5 minutes</strong>. If you didn't
          request this email, you can safely ignore it.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="footer">
        <p>Â© 2025 Wander Trip. All rights reserved.</p>
        <p>
          Discover personalized journeys with AI-powered recommendations and
          unforgettable experiences.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
